Class ProjectManagementCLI

Object
ProjectManagementCLI
public class ProjectManagementCLI extends Object
CLI interface for HDB Managers to create, view, and manage BTO projects. Features:
  • View all projects with optional filtering
  • View and manage own created projects
  • Create new projects with validation
  • Edit project attributes (dates, neighborhood, slots, flats)
  • Delete or toggle visibility of managed projects
Uses breadcrumbs for user navigation and shared filters by NRIC.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Javier
